<p>Consultant Laparoscopic &amp; Bariatric Surgeon at Wings Hospital, Surat. One of the pioneer of Wings Hospital. All kinds of Laparoscopy procedure are performed at Wings Hospital by Dr. Vikram Lotwala.<br />
<br />
